OL,5, The online bank Atom Bank has          
OL,6, introduced a four-day work week for its
OL,7, 430 staff without cutting their pay.   
OL,9,FEmployees now work 34 hours over four  
OL,10,Fdays and get Monday or Friday off, when
OL,11,Fpreviously they clocked up 37.5 hours  
OL,12,Facross the whole week.                 
OL,14,FBoss Mark Mullen told the BBC it was   
OL,15,Finspired by the pandemic and would help
OL,16,Fimprove wellbeing and retain staff.    
OL,18,FHowever, employees will have to work   
